description: Cool Dogz is all about Shaved Ice and what makes us different is that our shaved ice is made from premium ice and shaved into fluffy snow. It is not a crunchy snow cone, but rather a light, melt in your mouth shaved ice. All of our tropical flavors are made with premium concentrates and pure Hawaiian cane sugar. We never use high fructose corn syrup. Our shaved ice is gluten free, lactose free, fat free. Cool Dogz also features the amazing Flavor Station!! Imagine being able to create your own flavor combination!! The flavor station has 8 tropical flavors that allows kids and adults to add their own combination of flavors. You can’t miss the bright orange truck with the volcano spewing out shaved ice and the kite surfing Cool Dog!!
name: Cool Dogz Shaved Ice
